---
import PageLayout from '@/components/layout/PageLayout.astro';
import Container from '@/components/layout/Container.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '@/components/seo/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Service - Telluride Ski Hotels"
  description="Terms of Service for Telluride Ski Hotels. Read our booking terms, user agreement, and service policies."
>
  <Container class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Terms of Service', href: undefined },
    ]} />

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-12">Last Updated: November 14, 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            By accessing or using TellurideSki Hotels.com (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not use our services.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Your continued use of the Site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">2. Service Description</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Telluride Ski Hotels operates as a travel information platform and booking aggregator. We provide:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li>Real-time hotel availability and pricing information from third-party providers</li>
            <li>Booking facilitation through partnerships with accommodation providers including LiteAPI</li>
            <li>Travel guides, blog content, and destination information</li>
            <li>Activity booking through partners including Viator</li>
            <li>Ski conditions, weather, and trail map information</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            We act as an intermediary between travelers and accommodation/activity providers. The actual lodging, activities, and services are provided by third parties, not by Telluride Ski Hotels directly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">3. Booking Terms</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Reservations</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When you make a reservation through our Site:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li>You enter into a direct contractual relationship with the accommodation provider or activity operator</li>
            <li>You agree to the specific terms, conditions, and cancellation policies of that provider</li>
            <li>Payment is processed securely through our payment partners</li>
            <li>You will receive a confirmation email with booking details and provider contact information</li>
            <li>You must be at least 18 years old to make a booking</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Pricing & Availability</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Prices and availability displayed on our Site are provided by third-party suppliers and are subject to change without notice until booking is confirmed. We strive for accuracy but cannot guarantee that all information is current or error-free.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            All prices are displayed in USD unless otherwise noted. Taxes, resort fees, and other charges may apply and will be clearly disclosed before booking confirmation.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3 mt-6">Payment</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Payment processing is handled securely through encrypted connections. We accept major credit cards and other payment methods as displayed at checkout. By providing payment information, you confirm you are authorized to use that payment method.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">4. Cancellations & Refunds</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Cancellation and refund policies are determined by the individual accommodation provider or activity operator, not by Telluride Ski Hotels. These policies vary by property and reservation type and are clearly displayed during the booking process.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            To cancel a reservation:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li>Contact the property or provider directly using the information in your confirmation email</li>
            <li>Or contact our support team at hello@tellurideskihotels.com for assistance</li>
            <li>Review the specific cancellation policy for your booking before making changes</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            For detailed information, see our <a href="/cancellation-policy" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Cancellation Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">5. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When using our Site, you agree to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li>Provide accurate, current, and complete information during booking</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your account and password</li>
            <li>Use the Site only for lawful purposes</li>
            <li>Not attempt to interfere with the proper functioning of the Site</li>
            <li>Not use automated systems to access or scrape the Site without permission</li>
            <li>Respect intellectual property rights in our content</li>
            <li>Not impersonate others or provide false information</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Telluride Ski Hotels acts as an intermediary platform. To the fullest extent permitted by law:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li>We are not responsible for the quality, safety, or legality of accommodations or activities offered by third-party providers</li>
            <li>We make no warranties regarding the accuracy of pricing, availability, or property descriptions</li>
            <li>We are not liable for damages arising from your use of accommodations, activities, or services booked through our Site</li>
            <li>We are not responsible for force majeure events including natural disasters, extreme weather, pandemics, or other events beyond our control</li>
            <li>Our total liability for any claim shall not exceed the booking fee paid for the service in question</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            All content on this Site, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of Telluride Ski Hotels or our content licensors and is protected by copyright and trademark laws.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            You may view, download, and print content for personal, non-commercial use only. Any other use requires our prior written permission.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">8. Third-Party Links & Services</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Our Site contains links to third-party websites and integrates with third-party services (accommodation providers, activity operators, payment processors, mapping services, weather data providers, etc.).
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of service of these third parties. We encourage you to review their policies before using their services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">9. Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Your use of the Site is also governed by our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>, which explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">10. Governing Law & Disputes</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Colorado, United States, without regard to conflict of law principles.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the Site shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the American Arbitration Association rules, except where prohibited by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">11. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-200">
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@tellurideskihotels.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">hello@tellurideskihotels.com</a></p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:tellurideskihotels@gmail.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">tellurideskihotels@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700"><strong>Business Hours:</strong> Monday-Friday, 9am-5pm MST</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed text-center">
          <strong class="text-neutral-900">Questions or Concerns?</strong> We're here to help. Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:hello@tellurideskihotels.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">hello@tellurideskihotels.com</a> and we'll respond within 24 hours.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</PageLayout>

